2008;;Lady Godiva;;British;;Vicky Jewson;;Phoebe Thomas, Matthew Chambers, Natalie Walter;;romance/comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lady_Godiva_(film);;Jemima Honey, a teacher, needs to raise funds for her local creative arts centre. To do so, she accepts the challenge of businessmen and love interest Michael Bartle to ride through the streets of Oxford naked.